The paper discusses the use of AI and multimodal technologies for audio-visual scene-aware dialog, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The incorporation of an end-to-end audio classification ConvNet also suggests a focus on signal processing (cs.SD) and multimedia (cs.MM).
